    <h1 class="article-title">
        Everything Felt Like a Punishment
    </h1>
    <h2 class="article-subtitle">
        First-person accounts of COVID-19 from Stateville Correctional Center
    </h2>
    <p class="byline">
        By
        <a href="https://southsideweekly.com/author/madison-muller/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Madison Muller</a>
        and
        <a href="https://southsideweekly.com/author/cheyanne-m-daniels/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cheyanne M. Daniels</a>
    </p>
